Everyone will have an idea that can be transformed into a product but confused on how it can be done. Cynosure15 provides the first step towards its realisation.
You can express your idea that will be judged by an eminent panel.
10,+1,+2 students are eligible to participate.
Cash prizes worth Rs 6000  and Certificates will be given to winners.
For more details and online registration please visit\n\n
  www.cynosure15.com\n\n
Spot registration is also available.
For details contact:\n
